      CLEARWATER ROOF REPLACEMENT<br/><span class="gt">FREE ESTIMATES</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="max-w-2xl mx-auto" style="color:#555555;font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.75">
      Happy Roof provides full roof replacement in Clearwater, FL, from the beachside condos of Clearwater Beach to the family neighborhoods of Countryside. Shingle, metal, and tile options with an up to 15-year workmanship warranty and all permits handled.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 justify-center mt-8">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-t">Get a Free Estimate <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg></a>
      <a href="tel:8135957663" class="btn-o call-tracking-number">Call (813) 595-7663</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- INFO STRIP -->
<div style="background:#FFFFFF;border-top:2px solid #E6A817;border-bottom:1px solid #E0E0E0;padding:.85rem 0">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5">
    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-8 gap-y-2 font-display font-bold text-sm tracking-widest" style="color:#1A1A1A;text-transform:uppercase;font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif">
      <span>Clearwater, FL</span><span style="color:#E6A817">·</span><span>CCC1337380</span><span style="color:#E6A817">·</span><span>HappyRoof.com</span><span style="color:#E6A817">·</span><span style="color:#3B9FD9">(813) 595-7663</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- WHY SECTION -->
<section class="py-20" style="background:#FFFFFF">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-14 items-start">
      <div>
        <p class="sl gt mb-3">Why Replace Your Roof in Clearwater</p>
        <h2 style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:800;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);line-height:.95;color:#1A1A1A;letter-spacing:-.01em;margin-bottom:1.5rem">WHY CLEARWATER HOMEOWNERS CHOOSE A FULL ROOF REPLACEMENT</h2>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1.5rem">Clearwater stretches from the Gulf of Mexico beaches on its barrier island across the Intracoastal Waterway to the mainland neighborhoods of Clearwater proper. This geographic spread means roofing challenges vary dramatically within the same city. Beachfront properties along Mandalay Avenue face relentless salt spray and wind exposure, while inland neighborhoods like Countryside, Del Oro Groves, and Skycrest deal with the same punishing UV and afternoon thunderstorms that batter all of Pinellas County.</p>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1.5rem">Clearwater's housing stock includes everything from 1960s ranch homes with their original roofs in neighborhoods near Belcher Road, to newer subdivisions in Clearwater East, to the high-value waterfront properties of Island Estates and Sand Key. Many of these roofs are now 20 to 30 years old and showing signs of failure - granule loss on shingles, cracked tiles, rust on metal components, and underlayment that has dried out and lost its waterproofing ability. A full replacement restores protection, improves energy efficiency, and can significantly increase property value.</p>
        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:1.5rem">Happy Roof handles Clearwater roof replacements from start to finish: free inspection, material selection, permit coordination with the City of Clearwater and Pinellas County, professional installation, and final inspection. We hold Florida License #CCC1337380 and back every roof with an up to 15-year workmanship warranty. See our <a href="/clearwater-roofing" style="color:#3B9FD9;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600">Clearwater roofing page</a> for all services.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="scard p-6">
          <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><div><strong style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem">Architectural Shingles</strong><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.6;margin-top:.25rem">Owens Corning Duration HDZ rated for 130+ MPH winds - the most popular choice for Clearwater homeowners. Excellent durability and a wide selection of colors to match any home style.</p></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="scard p-6">
          <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><div><strong style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem">Standing Seam Metal</strong><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.6;margin-top:.25rem">Corrosion-resistant panels with Kynar finish, ideal for Clearwater Beach and Island Estates where salt air is constant. Reflects heat and lasts 40-60 years.</p></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="scard p-6">
          <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><div><strong style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem">Concrete & Clay Tile</strong><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.6;margin-top:.25rem">Extremely durable in Clearwater's climate with a 50+ year lifespan. Suits the Mediterranean and Florida-style architecture found in many established Clearwater neighborhoods.</p></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="scard p-6">
          <div class="check"><div class="check-dot"><svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#E6A817" stroke-width="3"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg></div><div><strong style="font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem">Up to 15-Year Workmanship Warranty</strong><p style="color:#555555;font-size:.9rem;line-height:1.6;margin-top:.25rem">Every Clearwater roof replacement comes with our written up to 15-year workmanship warranty in addition to the manufacturer's material warranty.</p></div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHAT'S INCLUDED / COMMON REPAIRS / WHAT WE CHECK -->
<section class="py-20" style="background:#F7F7F7">
