        <p style="color:#555555;font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.7">Complete removal of old roofing, thorough decking inspection, and replacement of any damaged plywood before new material is installed.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="scard p-8">
        <div style="width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;background:rgba(230,168,23,.1);margin-bottom:1rem">
