      <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">For properties on Clearwater Beach, Island Estates, and Sand Key, standing seam metal with a Kynar finish offers the best resistance to salt air corrosion. For mainland Clearwater homes, Owens Corning architectural shingles provide excellent wind resistance at a lower cost.</div></div>
    </div>
